{"tid":2217251,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"三名青年涉去年十月黃埔花園襲警罪成　還柙候判","createTime":"2020-09-25T09:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T18:16:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5bcf46597d4b940b6ac15f2a1ed5acfd76c6f4af","tid":2217251,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:55:22.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】三名青年涉嫌去年十月在紅磡襲警及對交通造成阻礙，在九龍城裁判法院被裁定罪名成立。<br />\n<br />\n三名被告介乎19至21歲，其中兩人是兄弟，涉嫌去年10月11日在黃埔花園堵路，並襲擊拘捕他們的便衣警員。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官梁嘉琪不接納辯方所指，被告在拘捕過程中，因為聽不到警員表明身分，以為持不同政見的人襲擊，認為其中一名被告被捕期間高叫「藍絲打人」，正正是因為他有參與堵路，裁定三人罪名成立。<br />\n<br />\n辯方呈上多封校長及家長的求情信，並指各被告紀律良好，因為社會情況作出與性格違背的事。<br />\n<br />\n法官押後至下月16日判刑，被告還柙期間會索取社會服務令及勞教中心等報告。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=406884\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406884&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=dd636747\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406884&h=af715043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=406884</a>"},{"pid":"319899e2e09c4b4c3051bfec36f609dc36c48f9f","tid":2217251,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:55:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9818&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=6b3c52ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9818</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第四庭<br />\n#梁嘉琪裁判官<br />\n#1011黃埔<br />\n#裁決<br />\n<br />\nD1鄧<br />\nD2伍<br />\nD3鄧<br />\n<br />\n速報...<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n1. 襲擊在正當執行職務的警員 (違反侵害人身罪條例 第36(b)條)<br />\n🛑罪名成立🛑<br />\n<br />\n2. 對公眾地方/交通造成阻礙 (違反簡易程序治罪條例 第4(8)條)<br />\n🛑罪名成立🛑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*法庭接納所有證人證供可靠誠實<br />\n*本案不涉及法律觀點是否知道警察身分，就辯方觀點稱第二證人襲擊D1-D3，沒有表明身份令他們以為是藍絲打人而自衛。法庭認為辯方說法矛盾。不認為D1-D3是一個控制的行為<br />\n<br />\n裁定三人兩項罪名成立<br />\n<br />\n🛑押後至10月16日兩點半九龍城第四庭C4判刑🛑<br />\n<br />\n為D1D2拿勞教、更生中心、社會服務令、兒童少年判罪評估報告，<br />\n為D3拿背景、社會服務令和勞教中心報告<br />\n<br />\n🛑押後期間三人需要還押🛑<br />\n<br />\n//辯方求情<br />\n<br />\n三人無案底，D1 D2 如今19歲，D3 21歲。<br />\n<br />\n就第二罪名，堵路時間30分鐘，引起不便一個小時多些，並非很嚴重罪行；<br />\n<br />\n就第一罪名，雖然就藍絲打人的說法法庭做了裁決，片段拍到PW3制服D2的情況，不論動作，或者所說的話，PW2都說不想動用武力，我給你走。明顯武力制服PW2後被告們很快收手，D1 D3於PW2糾纏時沒有進一步武力，有機會控制PW2都沒有進一步施以襲擊<br />\n<br />\n考慮報告希望考慮更生、勞教丶背景報告，希望考慮社會服務令<br />\n<br />\n求情信：<br />\nD1與D2中學校長求情信，校內好學生， 有紀律，第一被告做過足球隊隊長，D2做過資訊科技風紀。<br />\nD1專上教育學院的2名講師，正面評價，<br />\nD1 D3兩兄弟父母聯名信，乖仔，家庭學校都覺得他們乖。<br />\n<br />\n此前都有法官講過，基於任何政治意念，對社會不滿不能構成對犯法的求情因素，我無意圖這樣做。但明顯看到他們因為社會情況，作出與他們本身性格違背的事情，如非因為社會氣氛，很多年輕人不會夜晚出來做一些平常家庭不允許他們做的事。<br />\n<br />\n希望考慮行使武力時間短，雖然證人受傷不輕微，但因為其戴眼鏡，並不直接反映武力的嚴重性。無意說證人輕傷，只是戴眼鏡可能加重受傷程度<br />\n<br />\n希望閣下拿背景報告之餘拿社會服務令報告，D1D2希望拿勞教、更生中心報告；D3年紀勞教中心依然可收，不如D3拿背景、社會服務令和勞教中心報告。//<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"4d14825d1fb7f45d11fc0c638fba4396c121ad48","tid":2217251,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50cc643af3cbe62bdbcf7894742ee2845ee3194","tid":2217251,"uid":128514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"你又唔俾委任證，我點知你係差佬?"},{"pid":"40ee244c310c01b336ceafcf439540c48c320424","tid":2217251,"uid":207248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0398239fc714316103b1ea05fc54020657f5b5c","tid":2217251,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef883dab44850739487739c86ee67480ae37e51","tid":2217251,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0398239fc714316103b1ea05fc54020657f5b5c","tid":2217251,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7823e5a7f9ff2fd7eb3532aab30a6695945c67bd","tid":2217251,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0622a174a448cfbd95c3b10f9bb82aeada797a02","tid":2217251,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:00:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/YFGSNXKVMZHZXLVW4ZUIJY67MM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FYFGSNXKVMZHZXLVW4ZUIJY67MM%2F&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=2c341e1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FYFGSNXKVMZHZXLVW4ZUIJY67MM%2F&h=ae7fa0cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/YFGSNXKVMZHZXLVW4ZUIJY67MM/</a>"},{"pid":"be745e15158d511ab2ef76f168dd87db23bcaf33","tid":2217251,"uid":208568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5713a457cbe585016a8117dbf3cf57a6da2b3a6c","tid":2217251,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:02:27.000Z","msg":"裁判官梁嘉琪今裁決時引述徐的證供，指徐當時從後趕上三名被告，搭著兩兄弟被告的肩膊，有人打徐的背部，徐坦承不知誰人在背後襲擊他，惟身旁僅得三名被告，梁官認為徐的證供沒有誇大，是誠實可靠的證人。<br />\n<br />\n對於辯方質疑，徐見到三名被告用竹枝等物堵路時為何不拍照，梁官認為當時有200人聚集，可理解並非拍照的合適時機。<br />\n<br />\n梁官又稱，假若三名被告誠如辯方所言，在事發時沒有參與堵路，徐沒有透露其警察身份，何以被告會認定對方是立場不同的人而大叫「藍絲打人」，梁官認為辯方說法自相矛盾，裁定三名被告襲警、在公眾地方造成阻礙兩罪罪成。"},{"pid":"9f21020c4737b5d94b504b9bf8cb53620a369aff","tid":2217251,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:02:56.000Z","msg":"藍絲打人, 就好似班福建佬出黎打人咁, 根本唔會分你中立定咩就打"},{"pid":"1318f275213889f8154f0d759498eec825052d64","tid":2217251,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f50cc643af3cbe62bdbcf7894742ee2845ee3194","tid":2217251,"uid":128514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"你又唔俾委任證，我點知你係差佬?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"如果係打藍絲可能判得重重添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d3670d447a763d1507e297f148d323b4bc9669","tid":2217251,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1643b6ba8d88ffcd607d899098379292f77f01c","tid":2217251,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2aa8d07c132f7e6e1ff8a2a6a71ba91373e61c","tid":2217251,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:08:07.000Z","msg":"政治上呢個梁嘉琪同共匪台嗰個梁嘉琪就差得遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cbbbfe218266db7bd2969b185d21c34039bf7f","tid":2217251,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cfa62fc7f734fcf837bf6943d95ba449e1d4b6","tid":2217251,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5687b573cc0fa6f6f156fe63332e89ff90ffd4b4","tid":2217251,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62433381857829cdb6656c4904cbb23277031c43","tid":2217251,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07b4230f98c4e381ab403d4d026f4ad19fe6d5d","tid":2217251,"uid":364480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T18:16:22.000Z","msg":"法冶已死"}]}